## Welcome to my GitHub site!
### About Me
My name is Ethan Och (@REX647). I am a casual programmer, an avid gamer, and an aerospace enthusiast. My main interest lies in making small, useful programs that help with daily tasks or that simplify otherwise complex tasks.

### Programming Languages
I am most familiar with C++, though I have tinkered with Python, Lua, HTML, CSS, and C# in the past.

### Projects
